lines: Ndenda Ôndiwe Leza wangu, Mbuli Enoki wakale;
Ndijate mujanza lyako, Ndiswanganye muli ndiwe,
Nokuba nsiboni nzila, O Jesu ndeende andiwe.
Nsikonzyi kweenda endike, Myuwo ilaunga konse;
Ndiwe bukali bwa lwizi, O Mwami ndeende andiwe.
Na ndajata muli ndiwe, Nsikatolwi azya nyika;
Limwi Zioni nkabone, Muvuni ndeende audiwe.
